alice.respect.core

Class InternalOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • alice.respect.core.InternalOperation

  • public class InternalOperation
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an internal operation of a ReSpecT virtual machine. The possible argument of the operation is represented by a logic tuple
    Author:
    aricci
